<li id="cite_note-13"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint"><a href="#cite_ref-13">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text"><span class="ouvrage" id="Brittain1984"><span class="ouvrage" id="James_E._Brittain1984"><abbr class="abbr indicateur-langue" title="Langue : anglais">(en)</abbr> James E. <span class="nom_auteur">Brittain</span>, <span lang="en">«&#160;<cite style="font-style:normal;">Becker and Shive on the transistor</cite>&#160;»</span>, <i><span class="lang-en" lang="en">Proceedings of the IEEE</span></i>, <abbr class="abbr" title="volume">vol.</abbr>&#160;72, <abbr class="abbr" title="numéro">n<sup>o</sup></abbr>&#160;12,&#8206; <time>1984</time>, <abbr class="abbr" title="page(s)">p.</abbr>&#160;1695 <small style="line-height:1em;">(<a href="/wiki/Digital_Object_Identifier" title="Digital Object Identifier">DOI</a>&#160;<span class="plainlinks noarchive nowrap"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://dx.doi.org/10.1109%2FPROC.1984.13075">10.1109/PROC.1984.13075</a></span>, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/login.jsp?arnumber=1457343">lire en ligne</a>)</small><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Becker+and+Shive+on+the+transistor&amp;rft.jtitle=Proceedings+of+the+IEEE&amp;rft.issue=12&amp;rft.aulast=Brittain&amp;rft.aufirst=James+E.&amp;rft.date=1984&amp;rft.volume=72&amp;rft.pages=1695&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1109%2FPROC.1984.13075&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fieeexplore.ieee.org%2Fxpl%2Flogin.jsp%3Farnumber%3D1457343&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Ffr.wikipedia.org%3AWilliam+Shockley"></span></span></span>&#160;: <span class="citation">«&#160;... observation que William Shockley interpréta comme la confirmation de sa théorie du transistor à jonction...&#160;»</span></span>
